    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh, Bartholomäus Haller and János Dubraviczky to Banská
                    Štiavnica Town Council (Kremnica, 20 February 1541)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">They have some cases for which they need the Banská
                            Štiavnica town notary, Anton Paus. They ask that Paus is allowed to take
                            care of their affairs before he looks after those of the city.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Namhafft, ersam unnd waiß lieb hern unnd freundt!</p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Es sein ettlich sachen fur uns kumen, darzu wir euers
                    statschreibers, <persName>Anthonii Pausius</persName>,<note type="critic"
                        xml:id="note.1">In 1538, Anton Paus was preceptor in Banská Bystrica and
                        taught Ferenc Révay’s sons. From 1540, he became Town notary <hi
                            rend="italic">(Stadtschreiber)</hi> of Banská Štiavnica, and he was in
                        the service of the Thurzós and the Fuggers. See <hi rend="smallcap"
                            >Frankl</hi> 1873, 7–8; <hi rend="smallcap">Lichnerová–Špániová</hi>
                        2019; and <hi rend="smallcap">Kalus</hi> 1999, 290.</note> notturfftig wern.
                    Derhalben unnser beger, ir wölt denselben auffs erst zu unns auff die
                        <placeName>Cremnitz</placeName> verschaffen. Das wöl wir unns zu bescheen
                    verlassen, unnd thun, was euch lieb ist.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">Datum <placeName>Cremnitz</placeName> den XX. tag Februarii anno
                    Domini XXXXI<hi rend="super">o</hi>.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.4">
                    <seg type="signature">
                        <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Nicolaus Olahus custos Albensis
                            etc.</add>
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <p xml:id="p.5">
                    <seg type="signature">
                        <add corresp="author" type="insert">Bartholomes Haller von Hallerstain</add>
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <p xml:id="p.6">
                    <seg type="signature">
                        <add corresp="author" type="insert">Joannes Dubrawiczky etc.</add>
                    </seg>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso" xml:id="d.2">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p xml:id="p.7">Den namhafften, ersamen unnd weisen hern, richtern unnd rat der stat
                    Schemnitz, unnsern guten freundenn.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
